{"tid":40304,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"綠茶杏仁脆餅","createTime":"2016-12-15T06:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T13:38:04.000Z","uid":4456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aad5abf9500377f587643d3095443a46e98d8c5c","tid":40304,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尋日貼左紫薯, 今日唔爭在貼埋綠茶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3463.jpg?w=1462\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3463.jpg%3Fw%3D1462&h=aa454437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料 (約35塊)<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3429.jpg&h=3aa4ede9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全蛋\t1隻<br />\n低筋麵粉\t180g<br />\n糖霜\t75g<br />\n鹽\t1小撮<br />\n無鹽牛油\t90g<br />\n綠茶粉\t5g<br />\n杏仁片\t50g</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8fafaedae374820dcdef729e916b058190cf0bca","tid":40304,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1) 雞蛋打勻備用<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3430.jpg&h=3290e281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 無鹽牛油置室溫軟化後, 加入糖霜拌成忌廉狀<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3431.jpg&h=fe3ae21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 之後加入綠茶粉及鹽拌勻<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3432.jpg&h=70b5e5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 雞蛋分2-3 次加入, 拌至完全融合<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3434.jpg&h=b6daec7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5) 篩入麵粉拌成麵團<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3435.jpg&h=7a70ece5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6) 之後加入杏仁片拌勻, 隨喜好搓成長方型或圓型<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3439.jpg&h=2ddff9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=OtduVG5dQ3S%2FhgwDNjH6WgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=08334421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vlovecooking.com/</a> <br />\nblog: <a href=\"https://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=OtduVG5dQ3S%2FhgwDNjH6WgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=7add8669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vlovecooking.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f599429d502446b0f9ebeb176f1d66e4835cf71a","tid":40304,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"7) 用保鮮紙包好放入雪櫃(不是冰格) 一小時<br />\n<img src=\"https://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3444.jpg&h=65535a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8) 之後取出用刀切成 1cm 厚<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3446.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3446.jpg&h=909e86cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9) 放入己預熱170&deg;C 焗爐焗20分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3447.jpg&h=5c348651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10) 焗好後放到架上放涼<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3451.jpg&h=8d209b95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"210751442b0be0e0152164612fbe1f6e5f2ae871","tid":40304,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}